üåç Applications
	1.	Personalized Medicine
	‚Ä¢	Predict patient-specific drug metabolism (e.g., cyclosporine levels influenced by CYP3A5 variants).
	‚Ä¢	Tailor dosage recommendations using patient-specific genetic and metabolic networks.
	2.	Disease Risk Stratification
