	‚Ä¢	Capture not just ‚Äúrisk alleles‚Äù but their cascading effects in cellular pathways.
	3.	Synthetic Biology & Gene Editing
	‚Ä¢	Simulate concentrations of metabolites after CRISPR interventions.
	‚Ä¢	Optimize gene network designs for stability and yield (biomanufacturing, biofuels).
	4.	Pharmacogenomics Pipelines
	‚Ä¢	Predict drug clearance rates, toxicity thresholds, and therapeutic windows.
	‚Ä¢	Embed into hospital electronic medical records (EMRs) for real-time dosage adjustment.

