‚öñÔ∏è Limitations & Next Steps
	‚Ä¢	Data sparsity: Many gene‚Äìgene interactions remain unknown or weakly validated.
	‚Ä¢	Interpretability: Deep models capture nonlinear patterns but are often black-box‚Äîhybrid symbolic/neural approaches (like your Œ®(x) framework) are essential.
